00:24:56,536 --> 00:24:57,413
OF THE EXPERIENCE.

471
00:24:57,537 --> 00:24:59,957
HE WAS AN
EXCELLENT SCIENTIST

472
00:25:00,082 --> 00:25:02,376
AND TIRELESS
IN HIS PURSUIT
OF THE TRUTH.

473
00:25:02,500 --> 00:25:04,795
THAT COULD BE
WHAT DESTROYED HIM.

474
00:25:04,920 --> 00:25:06,046
POSSIBLE, CAPTAIN.

475
00:25:06,172 --> 00:25:08,132
EVIL DOES SEEK
TO MAINTAIN POWER

476
00:25:08,257 --> 00:25:10,384
BY SUPPRESSING
THE TRUTH.

477
00:25:10,508 --> 00:25:12,303
OR BY MISLEADING
THE INNOCENT.

478
00:25:12,428 --> 00:25:14,512
MISLEADING THE INNOCENT?

479
00:25:15,889 --> 00:25:16,514
I WONDER.

480
00:25:16,640 --> 00:25:20,518
DO YOU MEAN
THE CHILDREN
MAY BE INVOLVED?

481
00:25:27,067 --> 00:25:29,195
YES, DOCTOR.

482
00:25:29,320 --> 00:25:30,863
SPOCK...

483
00:25:30,988 --> 00:25:33,699
WHAT DO WE KNOW
ABOUT THE RACE
THAT LIVED HERE?

484
00:25:33,824 --> 00:25:35,368
ACCORDING TO THE LEGEND,

485
00:25:35,493 --> 00:25:38,037
TRIACUS WAS THE SEAT
OF A BAND OF MARAUDERS

486
00:25:38,162 --> 00:25:41,415
WHO MADE CONSTANT WAR
THROUGHOUT THE SYSTEM
OF EPSILON INDI.

487
00:25:41,539 --> 00:25:42,500
AFTER MANY CENTURIES,

488
00:25:42,624 --> 00:25:45,627
THE DESTROYERS
WERE THEMSELVES DESTROYED

489
00:25:45,752 --> 00:25:47,380
BY THOSE THEY
HAD PREYED UPON.

490
00:25:47,505 --> 00:25:47,796
IS THAT THE
END OF IT?

491
00:25:47,921 --> 00:25:49,423
NO.

492
00:25:49,547 --> 00:25:50,508
LIKE SO MANY LEGENDS,

493
00:25:50,632 --> 00:25:53,386
THIS ONE, TOO,
HAS A FRIGHTENING ENDING.

494
00:25:53,511 --> 00:25:56,763
IT WARNS THAT THE EVIL
IS AWAITING A CATALYST

495
00:25:56,889 --> 00:25:58,516
TO SET IT AGAIN
INTO MOTION

496
00:25:58,640 --> 00:26:01,643
AND SEND IT MARAUDING
ACROSS THE GALAXY.

497
00:26:03,937 --> 00:26:06,440
IS IT POSSIBLE

498
00:26:06,606 --> 00:26:10,027
THAT THE EVIL
FOUND THE CATALYST?

499
00:26:10,152 --> 00:26:13,197
I WAS SPEAKING
OF A LEGEND, CAPTAIN.

500
00:26:13,322 --> 00:26:15,741
BUT MOST LEGENDS HAVE
THEIR BASIS IN FACT, SPOCK.

501
00:26:15,866 --> 00:26:17,493
I THINK I
READ YOU, JIM,

502
00:26:17,617 --> 00:26:19,745
BUT AS MEDICAL OFFICER,
I MUST WARN YOU

503
00:26:19,870 --> 00:26:21,788
THAT UNLESS
THE NORMAL GRIEF

504
00:26:21,914 --> 00:26:23,416
IS TAPPED AND RELEASED

505
00:26:23,541 --> 00:26:24,750
FROM THESE CHILDREN,

506
00:26:24,875 --> 00:26:27,711
YOU ARE TREADING
DANGEROUSLY.

507
00:26:27,836 --> 00:26:30,964
I UNDERSTAND
YOUR DIAGNOSIS, DOCTOR,
AND I WILL RESPECT IT.

508
00:26:31,090 --> 00:26:34,343
BUT NOT TO THE EXCLUSION
OF THE SAFETY OF THE
ENTERPRISE, THANK YOU.

509
00:26:40,391 --> 00:26:42,226
SPOCK,
WHAT OTHER EXPEDITIONS

510
00:26:42,351 --> 00:26:44,019
HAVE VISITED TRIACUS?

511
00:26:44,144 --> 00:26:45,812
ACCORDING TO
FEDERATION RECORDS,

512
00:26:45,938 --> 00:26:46,980
THIS IS THE FIRST.

513
00:26:47,106 --> 00:26:49,149
WHAT WAS IT
PROFESSOR STARNES SAID

514
00:26:49,275 --> 00:26:51,402
ABOUT THE UNSEEN FORCE?

515
00:26:51,527 --> 00:26:54,447
HE SAID THAT AN UNSEEN
FORCE WAS INFLUENCING HIM,

516
00:26:54,572 --> 00:26:55,781
THAT HE RECOGNIZED IT,

517
00:26:55,906 --> 00:26:57,450
WAS BEGINNING
TO FIGHT IT,

518
00:26:57,575 --> 00:27:00,786
AND CANCELED HIS
REQUEST FOR A SHIP.

519
00:27:00,911 --> 00:27:02,371
A SHIP.

520
00:27:02,496 --> 00:27:03,872
YES, A SHIP
FOR TRIACUS,

521
00:27:03,997 --> 00:27:05,623
BUT WHY?

522
00:27:05,749 --> 00:27:07,501
BY WHOM?

523
00:27:07,625 --> 00:27:09,378
SECURITY DETACHMENT.

524
00:27:09,503 --> 00:27:11,964
READY FOR RELIEF
DUTY ON TRIACUS.

525
00:27:12,089 --> 00:27:13,840
ASSEMBLE IN
THE TRANSPORTER
ROOM IMMEDIATELY.

526
00:27:13,966 --> 00:27:16,260
I'LL HAVE SOME QUESTIONS
FOR THAT PLANET
DETACHMENT

527
00:27:16,385 --> 00:27:18,262
AS SOON AS
THEY'RE BEAMED UP.

528
00:27:18,387 --> 00:27:20,889
I THINK IT'S
ABOUT TIME WE FOUND OUT

529
00:27:21,014 --> 00:27:22,766
WHETHER
PROFESSOR STARNES'
ENEMY WITHIN

530
00:27:22,891 --> 00:27:24,684
IS ON THE
PLANET BELOW

531
00:27:24,810 --> 00:27:26,979
OR HERE ONBOARD
SHIP WITH US.

532
00:27:27,104 --> 00:27:28,564
COME ON.

533
00:27:41,619 --> 00:27:44,330
YOUR TOUR OF DUTY
WILL LAST ONE HOUR.

534
00:27:44,455 --> 00:27:46,373
BE PREPARED WITH
YOUR COMMUNICATORS
AT ALL TIMES

535
00:27:46,499 --> 00:27:48,334
TO REPORT
ANY ALIEN BEINGS.

536
00:27:48,459 --> 00:27:49,793
DON'T WAIT TO INVESTIGATE.

537
00:27:49,918 --> 00:27:51,629
BEAM DOWN THE GUARDS.

538
00:27:59,845 --> 00:28:01,514
BEAM UP
THE SECURITY DETACHMENT

539
00:28:01,639 --> 00:28:02,640
FROM TRIACUS.

540
00:28:09,980 --> 00:28:11,815
SPOCK.

541
00:28:15,319 --> 00:28:17,363
WHAT'S WRONG?

542
00:28:19,031 --> 00:28:21,867
I AM UNABLE TO
LOCK ON TO THE PROPER
COORDINATES, CAPTAIN.

543
00:28:21,992 --> 00:28:23,536
WHY NOT?

544
00:28:23,661 --> 00:28:26,997
IT APPEARS
WE ARE NO LONGER
ORBITING TRIACUS.

545
00:28:27,122 --> 00:28:28,874
THAT'S IMPOSSIBLE.

546
00:28:28,999 --> 00:28:31,585
IF WE'RE NOT
ORBITING TRIACUS,

547
00:28:31,709 --> 00:28:34,380
THEN THE MEN
I BEAMED DOWN...

548
00:28:34,505 --> 00:28:35,631
ARE DEAD.

549
00:28:35,755 --> 00:28:38,967
CAPTAIN,
WE ARE NO LONGER
ORBITING TRIACUS.

550
00:28:39,092 --> 00:28:42,304
ACTIVATE THE BRIDGE
MONITOR SCREEN.

551
00:28:51,397 --> 00:28:52,772
CAPTAIN TO BRIDGE.

552
00:28:52,898 --> 00:28:56,360
[KIRK]
MR. SULU, WE'RE NOT
ORBITING TRIACUS.

553
00:28:56,485 --> 00:28:58,945
WITH ALL RESPECTS,
CAPTAIN, YOU'RE WRONG.

554
00:28:59,071 --> 00:29:01,031
I HAVE TRIACUS
ON MY SCREEN NOW.

555
00:29:01,156 --> 00:29:03,576
YOU'RE OFF COURSE.
I'M COMING RIGHT UP.

556
00:29:03,701 --> 00:29:05,369
HAIL, HAIL,

557
00:29:05,494 --> 00:29:07,162
FIRE AND SNOW,

558
00:29:07,287 --> 00:29:09,248
CALL THE ANGEL.

559
00:29:09,373 --> 00:29:10,499
WE WILL GO

560
00:29:10,624 --> 00:29:11,958
FAR AWAY,

561
00:29:12,084 --> 00:29:14,086
FOR TO SEE,

562
00:29:14,211 --> 00:29:16,004
FRIENDLY ANGEL,

563
00:29:16,129 --> 00:29:17,381
COME TO ME.

564
00:29:17,506 --> 00:29:18,757
SULU!

565
00:29:18,882 --> 00:29:19,966
FIRE AND SNOW,

566
00:29:20,092 --> 00:29:21,927
CALL THE ANGEL.

567
00:29:22,052 --> 00:29:23,512
WE WILL GO

568
00:29:23,637 --> 00:29:24,930
FAR AWAY,

569
00:29:25,055 --> 00:29:26,682
FOR TO SEE.

570
00:29:26,806 --> 00:29:28,601
FRIENDLY ANGEL,

571
00:29:28,726 --> 00:29:30,310
COME TO ME.

572
00:29:48,662 --> 00:29:50,830
FRIENDS...

573
00:29:50,956 --> 00:29:53,667
WE HAVE REACHED
A MOMENT OF CRISIS.

574
00:29:53,792 --> 00:29:58,464
THE ENEMY HAVE DISCOVERED
OUR OPERATION...

575
00:29:58,589 --> 00:30:00,215
BUT THEY ARE TOO LATE.

576
00:30:00,340 --> 00:30:02,134
THEY NO LONGER
CONTROL THE SHIP.

577
00:30:02,259 --> 00:30:03,594
WE DO.

578
00:30:03,719 --> 00:30:05,512
WE SHALL PREVAIL.

579
00:30:05,638 --> 00:30:08,682
THEY WILL TAKE US
ANYPLACE WE DESIRE,

580
00:30:08,807 --> 00:30:11,393
SO BACK TO YOUR STATIONS.

581
00:30:11,518 --> 00:30:13,562
MAINTAIN YOUR CONTROLS.

582
00:30:13,687 --> 00:30:16,356
IF RESISTANCE MOUNTS,
CALL UPON THEIR BEASTS.

583
00:30:16,482 --> 00:30:19,109
THEIR BEASTS
WILL SERVE US WELL.

584
00:30:19,234 --> 00:30:21,528
THE FEAR IN
EACH ONE OF THEM

585
00:30:21,654 --> 00:30:24,490
IS THE BEAST
WHICH WILL CONSUME HIM.

586
00:30:24,615 --> 00:30:25,991
REMEMBER HOW IT WAS
ON TRIACUS?

587
00:30:26,116 --> 00:30:27,993
IF THEY RESIST,

588
00:30:28,118 --> 00:30:31,455
SO SHALL IT BE
ON THE<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

589
00:30:31,580 --> 00:30:34,874
IF YOU NEED ME,
CALL, AND I WILL APPEAR.

590
00:30:35,000 --> 00:30:38,211
OUR NEW GOAL
IS MARCOS 12.

591
00:30:38,337 --> 00:30:40,547
IT IS OUR NEW BEGINNING.

592
00:30:40,673 --> 00:30:43,258
WE MUST NOT FALTER.

593
00:30:50,974 --> 00:30:52,434
GO TO YOUR STATIONS.

594
00:30:52,559 --> 00:30:54,812
MARY, YOU REMAIN
HERE WITH ME.

595
00:31:08,074 --> 00:31:09,493
HELMSMAN,

596
00:31:09,618 --> 00:31:11,537
DISREGARD WHAT YOU
SEE ON THE SCREEN,

597
00:31:11,662 --> 00:31:14,873
WHAT YOU THINK
YOU SEE ON THE SCREEN.

598
00:31:14,998 --> 00:31:17,543
SET A COURSE
FOR STARBASE 4.

599
00:31:24,466 --> 00:31:26,844
HELMSMAN,
DID YOU HEAR ME?

600
00:31:26,968 --> 00:31:28,595
YES, SIR.

601
00:31:29,888 --> 00:31:31,931
LIEUTENANT UHURA,

602
00:31:32,057 --> 00:31:33,809
CONTACT STARBASE 4.

603
00:31:33,933 --> 00:31:36,520
TELL THEM WE'RE BRINGING
THE CHILDREN THERE.

604
00:31:36,645 --> 00:31:39,481
TELL STARFLEET COMMAND
I SUSPECT THEM

605
00:31:39,606 --> 00:31:41,191
OF BEING ALIEN
IN NATURE,

606
00:31:41,316 --> 00:31:43,902
AND I WANT A THOROUGH
INVESTIGATION MADE

607
00:31:44,027 --> 00:31:44,986
UPON OUR ARRIVAL.

608
00:31:45,111 --> 00:31:47,113
AYE, AYE, SIR.

609
00:32:01,587 --> 00:32:03,756
LIEUTENANT...

610
00:32:05,632 --> 00:32:07,760
WHAT ARE YOU
STARING AT?

611
00:32:07,885 --> 00:32:10,387
I SEE MY DEATH.

612
00:32:12,138 --> 00:32:14,808
A LONG DEATH.

613
00:32:14,933 --> 00:32:17,853
DISEASE AND PAIN.

614
00:32:17,977 --> 00:32:18,978
I SEE MY DEATH.

615
00:32:19,104 --> 00:32:21,398
LIEUTENANT...

616
00:32:21,523 --> 00:32:23,776
LIEUTENANT,
THERE'S NOTHING THERE.

617
00:32:23,901 --> 00:32:27,279
OH, GOD!
CAPTAIN,
DON'T LET IT BE.

618
00:32:29,322 --> 00:32:32,910
MR. SPOCK, YOU MAKE
THE CALL TO STARFLEET.

619
00:32:42,711 --> 00:32:46,465
MR. SULU, I ORDERED
YOU TO CHANGE COURSE.

620
00:32:57,309 --> 00:32:58,143
MR. SULU--

621
00:32:58,268 --> 00:33:00,604
CAPTAIN, STAY AWAY
FROM THE CONTROLS!

622
00:33:00,729 --> 00:33:03,649
IF YOU TOUCH THEM,
WE'LL BE DESTROYED.

623
00:33:03,774 --> 00:33:06,985
MR. SULU, THERE'S
NOTHING THERE!

624
00:33:08,320 --> 00:33:11,615
CAPTAIN, WHY ARE WE
BOTHERING STARFLEET?

625
00:33:20,499 --> 00:33:22,375
THAT WAS AN
ORDER, SPOCK.

626
00:33:22,501 --> 00:33:23,919
THIS BRIDGE IS UNDER
COMPLETE CONTROL.

627
00:33:24,043 --> 00:33:25,003
COMPLETE--

628
00:33:25,128 --> 00:33:27,756
THERE IS NO NEED.

629
00:33:29,633 --> 00:33:31,760
TAKE A LOOK
AROUND YOU.

630
00:34:05,002 --> 00:34:08,338
I CANNOT OBEY
YOUR ORDER, CAPTAIN.

631
00:34:36,992 --> 00:34:39,536
TAKE MR. SULU
TO HIS QUARTERS.

632
00:34:39,661 --> 00:34:41,120
HE IS RELIEVED
OF DUTY.

633
00:34:41,246 --> 00:34:42,539
[GARBLED SPEECH]

634
00:34:52,049 --> 00:34:54,593
[GARBLED SPEECH]

635
00:35:10,067 --> 00:35:10,984
FROM THE--

636
00:35:11,109 --> 00:35:11,944
CONFINE THEM--

637
00:35:12,069 --> 00:35:13,028
QUARTERS.

638
00:35:13,152 --> 00:35:14,654
CAN'T YOU HEAR ME?

639
00:35:16,907 --> 00:35:18,575
DID YOU HEAR ME?

640
00:35:47,980 --> 00:35:49,481
CAPTAIN...

641
00:35:49,606 --> 00:35:51,733
WE MUST GET OFF
THIS BRIDGE.

642
00:35:52,859 --> 00:35:54,820
YES, WE MUST.

643
00:35:54,945 --> 00:35:57,114
I'M LOSING COMMAND.

644
00:35:58,448 --> 00:36:01,242
I'M LOSING
MY ABILITY TO COMMAND.

645
00:36:02,410 --> 00:36:04,746
I'M LOSING
THE<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

646
00:36:07,582 --> 00:36:09,334
I'M LOSING COMMAND.

647
00:36:09,459 --> 00:36:11,878
I'M LOSING
THE<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

648
00:36:12,004 --> 00:36:15,132
MY SHIP IS
SAILING ON AND ON.

649
00:36:16,967 --> 00:36:18,635
I'M ALONE.

650
00:36:20,219 --> 00:36:21,930
ALONE.

651
00:36:22,055 --> 00:36:24,474
ALONE.

652
00:36:24,599 --> 00:36:27,102
I'M LOSING COMMAND.

653
00:36:27,226 --> 00:36:28,812
CAPTAIN.

654
00:36:28,937 --> 00:36:30,355
I'VE LOST COMMAND.

655
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:32,899
I'VE LOST
THE<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

656
00:36:33,025 --> 00:36:35,110
CAPTAIN KIRK.

657
00:36:37,403 --> 00:36:40,740
JIM.

658
00:36:52,961 --> 00:36:55,130
I'VE GOT COMMAND.

659
00:36:56,589 --> 00:36:59,092
I'VE GOT COMMAND.

660
00:37:02,179 --> 00:37:03,930
I'VE GOT COMMAND.

661
00:37:04,056 --> 00:37:07,017
CORRECT, CAPTAIN.

662
00:37:15,025 --> 00:37:16,902
WHERE TO, CAPTAIN?

663
00:37:17,027 --> 00:37:18,028
AUXILIARY CONTROL,

664
00:37:18,153 --> 00:37:20,488
MY VULCAN FRIEND.

665
00:37:20,613 --> 00:37:23,449
THIS SHIP
IS OFF COURSE.

666
00:37:27,037 --> 00:37:28,872
SCOTTY.

667
00:37:28,997 --> 00:37:30,874
I WANT YOU
TO OVERRIDE

668
00:37:30,999 --> 00:37:32,417
THE BRIDGE
NAVIGATION SYSTEM

669
00:37:32,542 --> 00:37:34,460
AND PLOT A COURSE
FOR STARBASE 4.

670
00:37:34,586 --> 00:37:36,171
I CAN'T DO THAT, SIR.

671
00:37:36,295 --> 00:37:37,338
WHY NOT?

672
00:37:37,463 --> 00:37:39,591
THESE ARE VERY
SENSITIVE INSTRUMENTS.

673
00:37:39,716 --> 00:37:42,052
I WILL NOT HAVE YOU UPSET
THEIR DELICATE BALANCE.

674
00:37:42,177 --> 00:37:44,846
WE WOULD ALL BE
LOST, FOREVER LOST.

675
00:37:52,104 --> 00:37:54,189
GO AWAY NOW.

676
00:37:54,313 --> 00:37:58,193
GO AWAY OR
WE'LL KILL YOU.

677
00:37:58,317 --> 00:37:59,736
SCOTTY, LISTEN TO ME.

678
00:37:59,861 --> 00:38:04,532
THE ENTERPRISE
HAS BEEN INVADED
BY ALIEN BEINGS.

679
00:38:04,657 --> 00:38:06,576
ITS DESTINATION
IS MARCOS.

680
00:38:06,701 --> 00:38:09,162
IF WE TAKE IT THERE,
MILLIONS WILL DIE,

681
00:38:09,287 --> 00:38:11,414
THE WAY THEY DIED
AT TRIACUS!

682
00:38:36,397 --> 00:38:37,190
OH, I'M ALL
RIGHT, SPOCK.

683
00:38:37,356 --> 00:38:40,068
MY BEAST IS FINISHED.

684
00:38:40,193 --> 00:38:41,319
IT WON'T RETURN.

685
00:38:41,444 --> 00:38:43,780
CAPTAIN, SO LONG
AS THE CHILDREN
ARE PRESENT,

686
00:38:43,905 --> 00:38:45,073
THERE IS DANGER.

687
00:38:45,198 --> 00:38:46,532
THEY ARE THE CARRIERS.

688
00:38:46,658 --> 00:38:48,952
SPOCK, THEY'RE NOT
THE ALIEN BEINGS.

689
00:38:49,077 --> 00:38:50,954
THEY'RE CHILDREN

690
00:38:51,079 --> 00:38:51,955
BEING MISLED.

691
00:38:52,080 --> 00:38:53,539
THEY ARE FOLLOWERS.

692
00:38:53,665 --> 00:38:55,917
WITHOUT FOLLOWERS,
EVIL CANNOT SPREAD.

693
00:38:56,042 --> 00:38:56,960
THEY'RE CHILDREN.

694
00:38:57,085 --> 00:38:59,462
CAPTAIN, THE
430 MEN AND WOMEN

695
00:38:59,587 --> 00:39:01,422
ON BOARD THE<i> ENTERPRISE</i>

696
00:39:01,547 --> 00:39:02,799
AND THE SHIP ITSELF

697
00:39:02,924 --> 00:39:04,801
ARE ENDANGERED

698
00:39:04,926 --> 00:39:06,094
BY THESE...CHILDREN.

699
00:39:06,219 --> 00:39:09,264
THEY DON'T UNDERSTAND

700
00:39:09,388 --> 00:39:11,432
THE EVIL THAT
THEY'RE DOING.

701
00:39:11,557 --> 00:39:12,433
PERHAPS THAT IS TRUE,

702
00:39:12,558 --> 00:39:15,812
BUT THE EVIL
THAT IS WITHIN THEM

703
00:39:15,937 --> 00:39:17,396
IS SPREADING FAST.

704
00:39:17,522 --> 00:39:19,316
AND UNLESS WE CAN FIND
A WAY TO REMOVE IT...

705
00:39:19,482 --> 00:39:22,443
WE'LL HAVE TO KILL THEM.

706
00:39:31,119 --> 00:39:33,412
CAPTAIN KIRK--

707
00:39:33,538 --> 00:39:34,497
WHAT IS IT, ENSIGN?

708
00:39:34,622 --> 00:39:35,581
I HAVE BEEN INSTRUCTED

709
00:39:35,707 --> 00:39:38,335
TO PLACE YOU AND
MR. SPOCK UNDER ARREST.

710
00:39:38,459 --> 00:39:39,169
BY WHOSE ORDER?

711
00:39:39,294 --> 00:39:41,046
STARFLEET COMMAND, SIR.

712
00:39:41,171 --> 00:39:42,797
WHERE DID YOU HEAR

713
00:39:42,922 --> 00:39:45,258
THIS ORDER, ENSIGN?

714
00:39:51,223 --> 00:39:53,432
NOW, LISTEN TO ME.

715
00:39:53,558 --> 00:39:55,393
THIS ORDER IS FALSE.

716
00:39:55,518 --> 00:39:58,897
I WANT YOU AND YOUR MEN
TO RETURN TO THEIR STATIONS.

717
00:39:59,022 --> 00:40:01,358
