AN ORDER, CAPTAIN.

725
00:40:35,058 --> 00:40:36,517
I KNOW THAT, ENSIGN.

726
00:40:36,642 --> 00:40:38,519
YOU HAVE NEVER
DISOBEYED AN ORDER,

727
00:40:38,644 --> 00:40:40,438
BUT AN ALIEN BEING
IS ABOARD THIS SHIP.

728
00:40:40,563 --> 00:40:42,523
I WILL NOT DISOBEY!
I CANNOT DISOBEY!

729
00:40:42,648 --> 00:40:43,900
ENSIGN, LISTEN TO ME!
YOU WILL DISOBEY THIS ORDER!

730
00:40:44,025 --> 00:40:46,069
STARFLEET COMMAND
SUPERSEDES YOUR ORDER, SIR!

731
00:40:59,999 --> 00:41:03,002
AHH...

732
00:41:06,423 --> 00:41:08,466
ENOUGH.

733
00:41:13,638 --> 00:41:15,514
TAKE THESE MEN
TO DETENTION

734
00:41:15,640 --> 00:41:30,738
THEN JOIN ME
ON THE BRIDGE.

735
00:41:36,077 --> 00:41:38,371
THE ENTERPRISE
WILL NEVER REACH
MARCOS 12.

736
00:41:38,496 --> 00:41:40,373
WE WILL NOT
BE LANDED THERE.

737
00:41:40,498 --> 00:41:42,375
THE CREW WILL TAKE US.
THE CREW BELIEVES.

738
00:41:42,500 --> 00:41:45,378
THE CREW...
DOES NOT UNDERSTAND.

739
00:41:45,503 --> 00:41:47,339
WHEN WE MAKE THEM
UNDERSTAND AS I UNDERSTAND,

740
00:41:47,464 --> 00:41:48,798
