YOU TO MARCOS!

741
00:41:48,923 --> 00:41:50,300
THEY WILL!

742
00:41:50,425 --> 00:41:51,259
WE ARE GOING
TO MARCOS!

743
00:41:51,384 --> 00:41:52,385
YOU WON'T! YOU WON'T.

744
00:41:52,510 --> 00:41:54,262
WE'RE GOING TO
FOLLOW OUR FRIEND!

745
00:41:54,387 --> 00:41:57,015
THEY WILL!

746
00:41:57,140 --> 00:41:59,100
YOUR FRIEND...
WHERE IS YOUR FRIEND?

747
00:41:59,225 --> 00:42:01,144
WHERE IS
THAT STOWAWAY?

748
00:42:01,269 --> 00:42:02,728
WHY DOES HE HIDE?

749
00:42:02,854 --> 00:42:05,231
HE WILL COME,
IF WE CALL HIM.

750
00:42:05,357 --> 00:42:05,940
BUT WE WON'T.
WE DON'T NEED HIM.

751
00:42:06,065 --> 00:42:09,902
WE'RE NOT
AFRAID OF YOU!

752
00:42:10,028 --> 00:42:12,864
