YOU'RE NOT AFRAID OF ME.

753
00:42:12,989 --> 00:42:15,867
BUT YOUR LEADER...

754
00:42:15,992 --> 00:42:17,118
IS AFRAID.

755
00:42:17,243 --> 00:42:18,619
WHAT'S HE AFRAID OF?

756
00:42:18,744 --> 00:42:20,413
HE'S NOT AFRAID
OF ANYBODY.

757
00:42:20,538 --> 00:42:21,289
HE'S NOT AFRAID
OF ANYTHING.

758
00:42:21,414 --> 00:42:23,582
HE'S AFRAID TO BE SEEN.

759
00:42:23,708 --> 00:42:26,085
AND WHEN THE CREW
SEES AND HEARS HIM,

760
00:42:26,211 --> 00:42:29,005
THEY'LL UNDERSTAND THAT
HE IS NOT THEIR FRIEND,

761
00:42:29,130 --> 00:42:30,673
AND THEY WON'T
FOLLOW HIM.

762
00:42:30,798 --> 00:42:32,591
HE IS OUR FRIEND.

763
00:42:32,717 --> 00:42:34,010
THEN LET HIM
SHOW HIMSELF.

764
00:42:34,135 --> 00:42:36,262
BRING HIM OUT!

765
00:42:36,388 --> 00:42:39,807
LET HIM PROVE TO ME
THAT HE IS MY FRIEND

766
00:42:39,932 --> 00:42:42,685
AND I'LL FOLLOW HIM TO MARCOS 12
AND TO THE ENDS OF THE UNIVERSE!

767
00:42:42,810 --> 00:42:44,562
NO!

768
00:42:48,816 --> 00:42:49,484
MR. SPOCK,

769
00:42:49,608 --> 00:42:52,362
PLAY BACK THE CHANT
THE CHILDREN SANG

770
00:42:52,487 --> 00:42:55,781
TO SUMMON UP
THE GORGAN.

771
00:42:56,574 --> 00:42:57,658
<i>[BEEPING]</i>

772
00:42:57,783 --> 00:42:59,660
<i>HAIL, HAIL,</i>

773
00:42:59,785 --> 00:43:02,414
<i>FIRE AND SNOW,</i>

774
00:43:02,539 --> 00:43:03,622
<i>CALL THE ANGEL.</i>

775
00:43:03,748 --> 00:43:05,124
<i>WE WILL GO</i>

776
00:43:05,250 --> 00:43:06,792
<i>FAR AWAY,</i>

777
