<i>FAR AWAY,</i>

785
00:43:21,849 --> 00:43:23,059
<i>FOR TO SEE.</i>

786
00:43:23,184 --> 00:43:24,769
<i>FRIENDLY ANGEL,</i>

787
00:43:24,894 --> 00:43:26,563
<i>COME TO ME.</i>

788
00:43:42,703 --> 00:43:44,163
THE TIME HAS COME

789
00:43:44,289 --> 00:43:45,582
TO SEE THE
WORLD AS IT IS.

790
00:43:46,916 --> 00:43:48,876
COME ON.

791
00:43:52,589 --> 00:43:55,674
WHO HAS SUMMONED ME?

792
00:43:55,800 --> 00:43:58,010
I DID, GORGAN.

793
00:43:58,136 --> 00:43:59,053
MY BEAST IS GONE.

794
00:43:59,178 --> 00:44:01,264
IT LOST ITS POWER

795
00:44:01,389 --> 00:44:03,682
IN THE LIGHT
OF REALITY.

796
00:44:03,808 --> 00:44:05,684
I COMMAND AGAIN,

797
00:44:05,810 --> 00:44:08,896
AND I ORDERED YOU HERE.

798
00:44:09,021 --> 00:44:10,273
NO, CAPTAIN.

799
00:44:10,398 --> 00:44:12,275
I COMMAND HERE.

800
00:44:12,400 --> 00:44:15,278
MY FOLLOWERS ARE
STRONG AND FAITHFUL

801
00:44:15,403 --> 00:44:17,238
AND OBEDIENT.

802
00:44:17,363 --> 00:44:19,657
THAT'S WHY WE
TAKE WHAT IS OURS

803
00:44:19,782 --> 00:44:21,909
WHEREVER WE GO.

804
00:44:22,034 --> 00:44:24,370
YOU TAKE FROM THOSE
WHO DO NOT KNOW YOU.

805
00:44:24,496 --> 00:44:26,456
AND WE KNOW YOU.

806
00:44:26,581 --> 00:44:28,916
THEN YOU KNOW
I MUST WIN, CAPTAIN.

807
00:44:29,041 --> 00:44:29,792
NOT IF WE JOIN
TOGETHER TO FIGHT YOU.

808
00:44:29,917 --> 00:44:31,877
