AND THAT IS
A GRAVE WEAKNESS.

813
00:44:40,803 --> 00:44:42,263
WE ARE ALSO VERY STRONG.

814
00:44:42,388 --> 00:44:44,307
AH, BUT YOUR
STRENGTH IS CANCELED

815
00:44:44,432 --> 00:44:45,766
BY YOUR GENTLENESS.

816
00:44:45,891 --> 00:44:47,435
YOU ARE
FULL OF GOODNESS.

817
00:44:47,560 --> 00:44:49,270
SUCH AS YOU
CANNOT BE CHANGED.

818
00:44:49,395 --> 00:44:52,273
YOU ARE LIKE
THE PARENTS.

819
00:44:52,398 --> 00:44:54,984
YOU MUST BE ELIMINATED.

820
00:44:58,488 --> 00:45:00,697
CHILDREN, I HAVE PICTURES
OF SOME OF YOU ON TRIACUS.

821
00:45:00,823 --> 00:45:03,326
I'D LIKE TO
SHOW THEM TO YOU.

822
00:45:03,451 --> 00:45:05,286
WOULD YOU LIKE
TO SEE THEM?

823
00:45:05,411 --> 00:45:08,164
MR. SPOCK, THE PICTURES.

824
00:45:08,289 --> 00:45:10,291
I FORBID IT.

825
00:45:10,416 --> 00:45:13,002
WHY SHOULD YOU FEAR IT?

826
00:45:13,127 --> 00:45:14,587
I FEAR NOTHING.

827
00:45:14,711 --> 00:45:16,922
SO WE WERE TOLD.
MR. SPOCK, THE PICTURES.

828
00:45:17,048 --> 00:45:18,841
THE CHILDREN ARE WAITING.

829
00:45:22,387 --> 00:45:25,598
<i>[LAUGHING]</i>

830
00:46:31,748 --> 00:46:33,541
THEY WOULD NOT
HELP TRANSPORT US.

831
00:46:33,666 --> 00:46:35,293
THEY WERE
AGAINST US.

832
00:46:35,418 --> 00:46:38,588
THEY HAD TO BE
ELIMINATED.

833
00:46:42,174 --> 00:46:43,968
<i>[BEEP]</i>

834
00:46:48,889 --> 00:46:50,349
TOMMY'S FATHER WOULD
HAVE DESTROYED YOU,

835
00:46:50,475 --> 00:46:52,226
BUT HE RECOGNIZED
YOU TOO LATE.

836
00:46:52,351 --> 00:46:54,895
AND YOU ARE
ALSO TOO LATE.

837
00:46:55,020 --> 00:46:58,023
THE KIND ONES
ALWAYS ARE.

838
00:46:58,149 --> 00:47:00,401
NOT ALWAYS, GORGAN.
NOT THIS TIME.

839
00:47:01,611 --> 00:47:03,529
YOU CAN'T HIDE FROM THEM.

840
00:47:03,655 --> 00:47:05,448
THEY SEE YOU
AS WE SEE YOU.

841
00:47:05,573 --> 00:47:07,908
THEY KNOW WHAT YOU ARE.

842
00:47:10,745 --> 00:47:12,204
EVEN THE CHILDREN LEARN.

843
00:47:12,330 --> 00:47:14,540
YOU ARE MY
FUTURE GENERALS.

844
00:47:14,666 --> 00:47:16,959
TOGETHER WE CAN RAISE
ARMIES OF FOLLOWERS.

845
00:47:17,084 --> 00:47:18,919
GO TO YOUR POSTS!

846
00:47:19,044 --> 00:47:21,297
THE FIRST
GREAT VICTORIES
ARE UPON US.

847
00:47:21,422 --> 00:47:23,257
YOU WILL SEE.

848
00:47:23,382 --> 00:47:25,593
WE HAVE MILLIONS
OF FRIENDS

849
00:47:25,718 --> 00:47:28,137
ON MARCOS 12.

850
00:47:28,262 --> 00:47:31,140
WE SHALL EXTERMINATE
ALL WHO OPPOSE US!

851
00:47:31,265 --> 00:47:34,185
OUR PURITY OF PURPOSE
CANNOT BE CONTAMINATED

852
00:47:34,310 --> 00:47:35,770
BY THOSE WHO DISAGREE,

853
00:47:35,894 --> 00:47:38,606
WHO WILL NOT COOPERATE,
WHO DO NOT UNDERSTAND.

854
00:47:38,731 --> 00:47:40,817
THEY MUST BE
ANNIHILATED.

855
00:47:40,983 --> 00:47:43,402
DON'T BE AFRAID.
LOOK AT HIM.

856
00:47:47,281 --> 00:47:49,033
WITHOUT YOU CHILDREN,

857
00:47:49,158 --> 00:47:50,535
HE'S NOTHING.

858
00:47:53,287 --> 00:47:55,581
THE EVIL REMAINS
WITHIN HIM.

859
00:47:57,458 --> 00:48:00,211
I COMMAND YOU!

860
00:48:00,336 --> 00:48:02,380
I COMMAND YOU!

861
00:48:02,505 --> 00:48:03,715
TO YOUR POSTS!

862
00:48:03,840 --> 00:48:05,675
CARRY OUT YOUR DUTIES

863
00:48:05,800 --> 00:48:08,302
OR I WILL DESTROY YOU!

864
00:48:08,427 --> 00:48:10,262
YOU WILL BE SWEPT ASIDE

865
00:48:10,388 --> 00:48:14,308
TO MAKE WAY
FOR THE STRONG.

866
00:48:14,433 --> 00:48:16,728
LOOK HOW UGLY
HE REALLY IS.

867
00:48:16,853 --> 00:48:19,230
LOOK AT HIM.
AND DON'T BE
AFRAID.

868
