00:49:00,062 --> 00:49:02,147
IT'S ALL RIGHT,
ISN'T IT, DOCTOR?

881
00:49:02,273 --> 00:49:04,191
YES. IT'S ALL RIGHT.

882
00:49:04,316 --> 00:49:06,485
WE CAN
HELP THEM NOW.

883
00:49:13,367 --> 00:49:15,244
MARCOS 12
DEAD AHEAD, SIR.

884
00:49:15,369 --> 00:49:16,662
REVERSE COURSE,
MR. SULU.

885
00:49:16,788 --> 00:49:18,497
AYE, SIR.

886
00:49:29,300 --> 00:49:31,761
COURSE REVERSED,
CAPTAIN.

887
00:49:34,971 --> 00:49:37,683
SET COURSE FOR
STARBASE 4, MR. SULU.

888
00:49:37,809 --> 00:49:39,811
